In the MATTER OF the Civil COMMITMENT OF E.B., SVP-724-15. (E.B. - Petitioner) C-927 September Term 2018
082755 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003821-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
